#: ../../A/AUP.rst:9
msgid ""
"Abbreviation, \"Acceptable Use Policy\". The policy of a given ISP which "
"sets out what the ISP considers to be (un)acceptable uses of its Internet "
"resources."
msgstr ""
"略語、「Acceptable Use Policy(利用規定)」。あるISPが、自社のインターネット資源の(不)適切な利用とみなすものを定めた方針。"
